import re

def extract_city_name(url):
    url = url.rstrip('')
    url = re.sub('^https?://', '', url)
    url = url.replace('www.', '')
    segments = url.split('/')
    city_name = segments[-1]
    city_name = city_name.replace('_', ' ')
    return city_name
